'''2015年阿富汗雪崩'''是發生於2015年2月24日至2月28日之間的[[雪崩|雪崩]]，地點位在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[潘傑希爾省|潘傑希爾省]]境內，造成至少310人喪生，129人受傷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/afghanistan/11443833/Avalanches-kill-more-than-180-in-Afghanistan.html|title=Avalanches kill more than 300 in Afghanistan|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2015-03-13|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321110634/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/afghanistan/11443833/Avalanches-kill-more-than-180-in-Afghanistan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。千名軍隊部署於潘傑希爾省進行救援<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/02/26/afghanistan-avalanche-toll-rises-to-162-amid-rescue-efforts/24045903/ | title=Afghanistan avalanche toll rises to 162 | work=USA Today | date=2015-02-26 | accessdate=2015-02-26 | author=AP | archive-date=2015-02-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227011142/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/02/26/afghanistan-avalanche-toll-rises-to-162-amid-rescue-efforts/24045903/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據潘傑希爾省臨時省長表示，此場災難為阿富汗三十年來最嚴重的雪崩<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-31619534 | title=Afghanistan's Panjshir hit by deadly avalanches | work=BBC | date=2015-02-25 | accessdate=2015-02-26 | archive-date=2015-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226204846/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-31619534 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
 
== 起因 ==
雪崩的起因是大型暴風雪襲擊潘傑希爾省<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/02/26/asia/afghanistan-avalanche/ | title=Death toll at 168 from Afghanistan avalanches | work=CNN | date=2015-02-26 | accessdate=2015-02-26 | author=Popalzai, Masoud | archive-date=2018-01-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180105011613/http://www.cnn.com/2015/02/26/asia/afghanistan-avalanche/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，這場暴風雪造成了部分地區積雪高度接近一公尺，使得救援工作遭到阻礙<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/25/afghanistan-avalanches-snow | title=Avalanches caused by heavy snow kill at least 124 people in Afghanistan | work=The Guardian | date=2015-02-25 | accessdate=2015-02-26 | author=Associated Press | archive-date=2015-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226190807/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/25/afghanistan-avalanches-snow | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

